snippet.title: Imperator: Rome - Release Date Announcement / Story Trailer
snippet.description:
The augurs have conferred and found the most auspicious date to release Imperator: Rome! You shall build the greatest empire the world has ever seen on April 25.

PRE-ORDER NOW ON THE STORE: https://pdxint.at/2RFMwbA 
PRE-ORDER NOW ON STEAM: https://pdxint.at/2S6Zswe

Paradox on YouTube:

Gameplay of our video games, convention coverage, and other fun things from Paradox!

Gameplay of our Grand Strategy Games. CK2, EU4, HOI4, Stellaris, and Imperator.
